So why does it seem like China

4
00:00:08,060 --> 00:00:10,600
is still selling oil to North Korea?

5
00:00:15,320 --> 00:00:16,740
Hi, welcome to China Uncensored.

6
00:00:16,750 --> 00:00:18,160
I’m Matt Gnaizda.

7
